# MMS V1.0 GENESIS - PART I: DOMAIN MODEL

**Document:** SPECIFICATION.md - Part I
**Version:** 1.0.0
**Date:** 2026-01-06
**Status:** Production Ready

---

## Table of Contents

1. [Railway Maintenance Domain](#1-railway-maintenance-domain)
   - 1.1 ECM Framework (EU 2019/779)
   - 1.2 RAMS Compliance (EN 50126-1)
   - 1.3 EN 15380 Railway Terminology
2. [Dubai Metro Context](#2-dubai-metro-context)
   - 2.1 Fleet Composition
