| Quantity | 49 trains (newer fleet) |
| Train Designation | KNK-001 through KNK-049 |
| Cars per Train | 5 |
| Base Mileage Range | 320,000 - 600,000 km |
| Assigned Depot | Jebel Ali |
| Line Assignment | Green Line |

---

### 2.2 Depot Configuration

#### 2.2.1 Depot Specifications

| Depot ID | Name | Location | Maintenance Tracks | Weekly Man-Hours | Serves |
|----------|------|----------|-------------------|------------------|--------|
| depot-red | Al Rashidiya | Red Line terminus | 5 | 2,800 | Alstom fleet |
| depot-green | Jebel Ali | Green Line terminus | 4 | 2,400 | Kinki Sharyo fleet |

#### 2.2.2 Combined Resources

