### 5.3 Maintenance Triggers

| Trigger Type | Description | Best For | Limitations |
|--------------|-------------|----------|-------------|
| Time-based | Calendar intervals (e.g., monthly) | Simple assets, regulatory compliance | Over/under maintenance |
| Mileage-based | Odometer intervals (primary) | Wear-dependent components | Tracking complexity |
| Condition-based | Sensor thresholds | Critical components | Sensor infrastructure |
| Hybrid | Combined triggers | Most applications | Implementation complexity |

**V1.0 Implementation:** Mileage-based only (primary trigger type for Dubai Metro).

