### 3.4 Conflict Representation

#### 3.4.1 Conflict Detection Formula

A conflict exists between Task A and Task B if:

```
Overlap Conflict:
  (A.startDay <= B.startDay + B.duration) AND
  (A.startDay + A.duration >= B.startDay) AND
  (A.trainId == B.trainId)

Resource Conflict (Future):
  Sum(tasks requiring track T on date D) > Track.capacity
```

#### 3.4.2 Conflict Entity (Future)

```typescript
/**
 * Conflict entity for explicit conflict tracking.
 * V1.0 uses Task.hasConflict flag; this entity is for V1.1+.
 */
export interface Conflict {
  /** Unique conflict identifier */
  id: string;

  /** Pair of conflicting task IDs */
  taskIds: [string, string];

  /** Conflict type classification */
  type: 'overlap' | 'resource' | 'dependency';

  /** Severity for prioritization */
  severity: 'low' | 'medium' | 'high';

  /** Human-readable description */
  description?: string;
}
```

